practitioners of magic

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:55.810 align:middle line:84%
encourage others to
approach the magical life

00:10:55.810 --> 00:10:58.450 align:middle line:84%
as a serious modern
spiritual path

00:10:58.450 --> 00:11:00.520 align:middle line:84%
in order to really
benefit from all

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:03.880 align:middle line:84%
it has to offer in one's own
life and one's relationship

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:07.440 align:middle line:84%
to the world and
universe at large.

